Extrapolation to N=6144
========================================================================
Reference point: nmesh=384, per-tile=20.605s, mem=2539 MB

Projected full-run cost on a SINGLE GPU using this nmesh:
nmesh_t    ntile_t    tiles_tot    wall_1GPU(h)   wall_8GPU(h)  
384        17         4913         28.12          3.52          
256        26         17576        32.55          4.07          
